Clear Film Protect for Device LCD Screen

Recommend order 3pcs, if stick failed and try more. 


  • Highly transparent, so don't worry that will effect your viewing
  • 3 layers of PET film, total thickness 0.25mm, using layer: 0.125mm (Higher Sensitivity)
  • Made of imported Taiwan PET Material
  • Anti-dust, Anti-scratch
  • Attaches smoothly with self-adhering surface; leaves no residue when removed.
  • A item send 1 Screen Cleaning Wipe only
     

Installation Instruction:

Step 1. Use the screen wipes to clean fingerprint,dust, oil ,spots and dirt on the LCD screen, please remember to be sure wiping before hands on the film.

Step 2. Pull down a part of 1st film.

Step 3. Make the electrostatic adsorption levels target to the screen position of neat film and tear out 1stfilm.

Step 4. After the film adsorpted,pull down the 2nd film.

Step 5. Tear the protective stickers with attachments directly paste to. So you're done!

Note:

  • More Screen Protector Film style, pls click here.
  • If need large quantity order, please contact us.

Clear Film Protect for Device LCD Screen

Recommend order 3pcs, if stick failed and try more. 


  • Highly transparent, so don't worry that will effect your viewing
  • 3 layers of PET film, total thickness 0.25mm, using layer: 0.125mm (Higher Sensitivity)
  • Made of imported Taiwan PET Material
  • Anti-dust, Anti-scratch
  • Attaches smoothly with self-adhering surface; leaves no residue when removed.
  • A item send 1 Screen Cleaning Wipe only
     

Installation Instruction:

Step 1. Use the screen wipes to clean fingerprint,dust, oil ,spots and dirt on the LCD screen, please remember to be sure wiping before hands on the film.

Step 2. Pull down a part of 1st film.

Step 3. Make the electrostatic adsorption levels target to the screen position of neat film and tear out 1stfilm.

Step 4. After the film adsorpted,pull down the 2nd film.

Step 5. Tear the protective stickers with attachments directly paste to. So you're done!

Recommend order 3pcs, if stick failed and try more. 


  • Highly transparent, so don't worry that will effect your viewing
  • 3 layers of PET film, total thickness 0.25mm, using layer: 0.125mm (Higher Sensitivity)
  • Made of imported Taiwan PET Material
  • Anti-dust, Anti-scratch
  • Attaches smoothly with self-adhering surface; leaves no residue when removed.
  • A item send 1 Screen Cleaning Wipe only
     

Installation Instruction:

Step 1. Use the screen wipes to clean fingerprint,dust, oil ,spots and dirt on the LCD screen, please remember to be sure wiping before hands on the film.

Step 2. Pull down a part of 1st film.

Step 3. Make the electrostatic adsorption levels target to the screen position of neat film and tear out 1stfilm.

Step 4. After the film adsorpted,pull down the 2nd film.

Step 5. Tear the protective stickers with attachments directly paste to. So you're done!

Clear Film Protect for Device LCD Screen

Recommend order 3pcs, if stick failed and try more. 


  • Highly transparent, so don't worry that will effect your viewing
  • 3 layers of PET film, total thickness 0.25mm, using layer: 0.125mm (Higher Sensitivity)
  • Made of imported Taiwan PET Material
  • Anti-dust, Anti-scratch
  • Attaches smoothly with self-adhering surface; leaves no residue when removed.
  • A item send 1 Screen Cleaning Wipe only
     

Installation Instruction:

Step 1. Use the screen wipes to clean fingerprint,dust, oil ,spots and dirt on the LCD screen, please remember to be sure wiping before hands on the film.

Step 2. Pull down a part of 1st film.

Step 3. Make the electrostatic adsorption levels target to the screen position of neat film and tear out 1stfilm.

Step 4. After the film adsorpted,pull down the 2nd film.

Step 5. Tear the protective stickers with attachments directly paste to. So you're done!

Clear Film Protect for Device LCD Screen

Recommend order 3pcs, if stick failed and try more. 


  • Highly transparent, so don't worry that will effect your viewing
  • 3 layers of PET film, total thickness 0.25mm, using layer: 0.125mm (Higher Sensitivity)
  • Made of imported Taiwan PET Material
  • Anti-dust, Anti-scratch
  • Attaches smoothly with self-adhering surface; leaves no residue when removed.
  • A item send 1 Screen Cleaning Wipe only
     

Installation Instruction:

Step 1. Use the screen wipes to clean fingerprint,dust, oil ,spots and dirt on the LCD screen, please remember to be sure wiping before hands on the film.

Step 2. Pull down a part of 1st film.

Step 3. Make the electrostatic adsorption levels target to the screen position of neat film and tear out 1stfilm.

Step 4. After the film adsorpted,pull down the 2nd film.

Step 5. Tear the protective stickers with attachments directly paste to. So you're done!

Clear Film Protect for Device LCD Screen

Recommend order 3pcs, if stick failed and try more. 


  • Highly transparent, so don't worry that will effect your viewing
  • 3 layers of PET film, total thickness 0.25mm, using layer: 0.125mm (Higher Sensitivity)
  • Made of imported Taiwan PET Material
  • Anti-dust, Anti-scratch
  • Attaches smoothly with self-adhering surface; leaves no residue when removed.
  • A item send 1 Screen Cleaning Wipe only
     

Installation Instruction:

Step 1. Use the screen wipes to clean fingerprint,dust, oil ,spots and dirt on the LCD screen, please remember to be sure wiping before hands on the film.

Step 2. Pull down a part of 1st film.

Step 3. Make the electrostatic adsorption levels target to the screen position of neat film and tear out 1stfilm.

Step 4. After the film adsorpted,pull down the 2nd film.

Step 5. Tear the protective stickers with attachments directly paste to. So you're done!

  • Highly transparent, so don't worry that will effect your viewing
  • 3 layers of PET film, total thickness 0.25mm, using layer: 0.125mm (Higher Sensitivity)
  • Made of imported Taiwan PET Material
  • Anti-dust, Anti-scratch
  • Attaches smoothly with self-adhering surface; leaves no residue when removed.
  • A item send 1 Screen Cleaning Wipe only
     

Installation Instruction:

Step 1. Use the screen wipes to clean fingerprint,dust, oil ,spots and dirt on the LCD screen, please remember to be sure wiping before hands on the film.

Step 2. Pull down a part of 1st film.

Step 3. Make the electrostatic adsorption levels target to the screen position of neat film and tear out 1stfilm.

Step 4. After the film adsorpted,pull down the 2nd film.

Step 5. Tear the protective stickers with attachments directly paste to. So you're done!

Note:

  • More Screen Protector Film style, pls click here.
  • If need large quantity order, please contact us.

Recommend order 3pcs, if stick failed and try more. 


  • Highly transparent, so don't worry that will effect your viewing
  • 3 layers of PET film, total thickness 0.25mm, using layer: 0.125mm (Higher Sensitivity)
  • Made of imported Taiwan PET Material
  • Anti-dust, Anti-scratch
  • Attaches smoothly with self-adhering surface; leaves no residue when removed.
  • A item send 1 Screen Cleaning Wipe only
     

Installation Instruction:

Step 1. Use the screen wipes to clean fingerprint,dust, oil ,spots and dirt on the LCD screen, please remember to be sure wiping before hands on the film.

Step 2. Pull down a part of 1st film.

Step 3. Make the electrostatic adsorption levels target to the screen position of neat film and tear out 1stfilm.

Step 4. After the film adsorpted,pull down the 2nd film.

Step 5. Tear the protective stickers with attachments directly paste to. So you're done!

Clear Film Protect for Device LCD Screen

Recommend order 3pcs, if stick failed and try more. 


  • Highly transparent, so don't worry that will effect your viewing
  • 3 layers of PET film, total thickness 0.25mm, using layer: 0.125mm (Higher Sensitivity)
  • Made of imported Taiwan PET Material
  • Anti-dust, Anti-scratch
  • Attaches smoothly with self-adhering surface; leaves no residue when removed.
  • A item send 1 Screen Cleaning Wipe only
     

Installation Instruction:

Step 1. Use the screen wipes to clean fingerprint,dust, oil ,spots and dirt on the LCD screen, please remember to be sure wiping before hands on the film.

Step 2. Pull down a part of 1st film.

Step 3. Make the electrostatic adsorption levels target to the screen position of neat film and tear out 1stfilm.

Step 4. After the film adsorpted,pull down the 2nd film.

Step 5. Tear the protective stickers with attachments directly paste to. So you're done!

Clear Film Protect for Device LCD Screen

Recommend order 3pcs, if stick failed and try more. 


  • Highly transparent, so don't worry that will effect your viewing
  • 3 layers of PET film, total thickness 0.25mm, using layer: 0.125mm (Higher Sensitivity)
  • Made of imported Taiwan PET Material
  • Anti-dust, Anti-scratch
  • Attaches smoothly with self-adhering surface; leaves no residue when removed.
  • A item send 1 Screen Cleaning Wipe only
     

Installation Instruction:

Step 1. Use the screen wipes to clean fingerprint,dust, oil ,spots and dirt on the LCD screen, please remember to be sure wiping before hands on the film.

Step 2. Pull down a part of 1st film.

Step 3. Make the electrostatic adsorption levels target to the screen position of neat film and tear out 1stfilm.

Step 4. After the film adsorpted,pull down the 2nd film.

Step 5. Tear the protective stickers with attachments directly paste to. So you're done!

Clear Film Protect for Device LCD Screen

Recommend order 3pcs, if stick failed and try more. 


  • Highly transparent, so don't worry that will effect your viewing
  • 3 layers of PET film, total thickness 0.25mm, using layer: 0.125mm (Higher Sensitivity)
  • Made of imported Taiwan PET Material
  • Anti-dust, Anti-scratch
  • Attaches smoothly with self-adhering surface; leaves no residue when removed.
  • A item send 1 Screen Cleaning Wipe only
     

Installation Instruction:

Step 1. Use the screen wipes to clean fingerprint,dust, oil ,spots and dirt on the LCD screen, please remember to be sure wiping before hands on the film.

Step 2. Pull down a part of 1st film.

Step 3. Make the electrostatic adsorption levels target to the screen position of neat film and tear out 1stfilm.

Step 4. After the film adsorpted,pull down the 2nd film.

Step 5. Tear the protective stickers with attachments directly paste to. So you're done!

Clear Film Protect for Device LCD Screen

Recommend order 3pcs, if stick failed and try more. 


  • Highly transparent, so don't worry that will effect your viewing
  • 3 layers of PET film, total thickness 0.25mm, using layer: 0.125mm (Higher Sensitivity)
  • Made of imported Taiwan PET Material
  • Anti-dust, Anti-scratch
  • Attaches smoothly with self-adhering surface; leaves no residue when removed.
  • A item send 1 Screen Cleaning Wipe only
     

Installation Instruction:

Step 1. Use the screen wipes to clean fingerprint,dust, oil ,spots and dirt on the LCD screen, please remember to be sure wiping before hands on the film.

Step 2. Pull down a part of 1st film.

Step 3. Make the electrostatic adsorption levels target to the screen position of neat film and tear out 1stfilm.

Step 4. After the film adsorpted,pull down the 2nd film.

Step 5. Tear the protective stickers with attachments directly paste to. So you're done!

Note:

  • If need large quantity order, please contact us.
